## Impact on the Social Media Platform  

| Aspect                          | Impact Description                                                                                         |
|--------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Platform Purpose & Value**   | Enhances Instagram's role from a photo-sharing app to a holistic social well-being platform without losing core value of visual storytelling. |
| **User Base**                  | Attracts more health-conscious users, mental health advocates, and diverse demographics seeking meaningful connections. |
| **Business Model**             | May require balancing ad revenue with user well-being; potential for new revenue streams via premium mental health services or community features. |
| **User Engagement**            | Shifts from passive scrolling to active, mindful participation, improving long-term retention and satisfaction. |
| **Reputation & Trust**         | Positions Instagram as a leader in ethical social media, potentially influencing industry standards.        |

